{"tid":1761030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"街坊歡呼奠酒「祭」周浩鼎","createTime":"2019-11-28T15:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T15:40:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eecfe098164830bb0b875f06415aba1d271243fe","tid":1761030,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T15:25:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191126/K6QQCQHOL57GC2TMJD7XASPJLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191126%2FK6QQCQHOL57GC2TMJD7XASPJLU%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=289dd3be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191126%2FK6QQCQHOL57GC2TMJD7XASPJLU%2F&h=16bbc37c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191126/K6QQCQHOL57GC2TMJD7XASPJLU/</a><br />\n<br />\n街坊歡呼奠酒「祭」周浩鼎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191126/large/1574703397_b470.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191126%2Flarge%2F1574703397_b470.gif&h=1021641a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n富東市民舉杯送別周浩鼎。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨晚上9時許，約50名街坊響應網上號召，帶備香檳、紅酒及薯片等，到周浩鼎位於東涌富東邨的辦事處外開香檳慶祝，有人為其奠酒，並高呼「飲杯，一路好走」，街坊大聲歡呼，當然少不了請「小鳳姐」出場，播放《喜氣洋洋》，市民齊唱「熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱」，氣氛高漲。<br />\n黎敬中攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191126/large/1574703396_5b82.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191126%2Flarge%2F1574703396_5b82.gif&h=b5a44b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人奠酒「慶祝」周浩鼎當選「2019區議會落選人」。"},{"pid":"58cb2d6298b284d384dd4df1c50129889850cfa4","tid":1761030,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T15:40:08.000Z","msg":"可喜可賀～～～～<br />\n<br />\n最好入埋棺材"}]}